                            (one for each partner) provides four critical
                            advantages over a single-policy approach:
                        </p>

                        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 my-16">
                            <div
                                class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[40px] border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all"
                            >
                                <h4
                                    class="text-xl font-bold flex items-center gap-3 mb-4"
                                >
                                    <span
                                        class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-50 text-[#C41E3A] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center font-black"
                                        >01</span
                                    >
                                    Double the Tax Deduction
                                </h4>
                                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                                    Both partners can contribute up to CHF 7,056
                                    annually (2025 limit), totaling <strong
                                        >CHF 14,112</strong
                                    > for the household. This can mean CHF 4,000+
                                    in annual tax savings.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[40px] border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all"
                            >
                                <h4
                                    class="text-xl font-bold flex items-center gap-3 mb-4"
                                >
                                    <span
                                        class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-50 text-[#C41E3A] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center font-black"
                                        >02</span
                                    >
                                    Double the Protection
                                </h4>
                                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                                    If something happens to one partner, the
                                    other's 3a remains untouched and
                                    independent. Each partner's life insurance
                                    coverage is tailored to their specific
                                    income and role.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[40px] border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all"
                            >
                                <h4
                                    class="text-xl font-bold flex items-center gap-3 mb-4"
                                >
                                    <span
                                        class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-50 text-[#C41E3A] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center font-black"
                                        >03</span
                                    >
                                    Independent Flexibility
                                </h4>
                                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                                    Each partner can choose their own investment
                                    strategy. One may prefer high-equity growth,
                                    while the other prioritizes capital
                                    guarantees for the mortgage.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[40px] border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all"
                            >
                                <h4
                                    class="text-xl font-bold flex items-center gap-3 mb-4"
                                >
                                    <span
                                        class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-50 text-[#C41E3A] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center font-black"
                                        >04</span
                                    >
                                    Separate Beneficiaries
                                </h4>
                                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
